inquiries.query:
/*
In the company_dim table find all company names that include 'Tech' immediately followed by any single character. 
Return the name column.
*/

/*
-- 1.first any char , Tech , single char
SELECT name
FROM company_dim
WHERE name LIKE '%Tech_';

-- 2.single char, Tech , single char
SELECT name
FROM company_dim
WHERE name REGEXP 'Tech.';

-- 3. Tech , any char 
SELECT name
FROM company_dim
WHERE name LIKE 'Tech%';
inquiries.name: wild problem -1
